      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Do you service diesel trucks?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes. We work on both gas and diesel light-duty and medium-duty trucks. Many Eckville-area residents drive diesel pickups for farm and oilfield work, and we're equipped to handle them."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Can I wait while my vehicle is serviced?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes. We have a comfortable waiting room with Wi-Fi, TV, and complimentary beverages and snacks. For longer services, we can arrange a shuttle within Sylvan Lake, or you can explore town while you wait."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Do you do out-of-province inspections?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes. We're a licensed AMVIC facility for out-of-province vehicle inspections. This is a common need in the Eckville area, especially for vehicles purchased from BC or Saskatchewan. We handle the full inspection and paperwork."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What's covered under the NAPA warranty?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "The NAPA Peace of Mind warranty covers qualifying repairs for 24 months or 40,000 km, whichever comes first. It's honoured at over 17,000 NAPA AUTOPRO and AutoCare locations across North America — so you're covered whether you're in Eckville, Edmonton, or on vacation."
